    <item>
      <title>德意志银行在新的成本逆风中将邮政银行工资提高 12.5%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/deutsche-bank-raises-postbank-pay-by-12-5-in-new-cost-headwind</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德意志银行已同意将其大量德国员工的工资提高 12.5%，这增加了首席执行官 Christian Sewing 的成本压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/deutsche-bank-raises-postbank-pay-by-12-5-in-new-cost-headwind</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 09:24:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于买家在陷入困境的市场中观望，可可再次暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/cocoa-slumps-again-as-buyers-hold-back-in-troubled-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于流动性枯竭且商业买家不愿购买可可豆，可可价格再次下跌，持续一周的剧烈波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/cocoa-slumps-again-as-buyers-hold-back-in-troubled-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 09:14:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行账户表明日本将在美联储周内第二次干预日元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/boj-accounts-signal-japan-s-second-yen-intervention-in-fed-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博对央行账户的分析显示，日本可能本周进行了第二次货币干预，这是其加强支撑日元力度的又一迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/boj-accounts-signal-japan-s-second-yen-intervention-in-fed-week</guid>
